<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.3">
<l>poṅkuveṇma ṇalkoṇṭu ciṟṟilum muṟṟatti ḻaikkaluṟil</l>
<l>caṅkucak karamtaṇṭu vāḷvillu mallati ḻaikkaluṟāḷ</l>
<l>koṅkaiyiṉ ṉamkuvinte ḻuntila kōvin taṉōṭivaḷai</l>
<l>caṅkaiyāki yeṉṉuḷḷam nāḷtoṟum taṭṭuḷup pākiṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [before she] was making toy houses</l>
<l rend="indent">with piles of white sand in the courtyard,</l>
<l>[now she] is making nothing but [His] conch,</l>
<l rend="indent">discus, staff, sword, and bow!</l>
<l>[Her] breast [have] not [even] grown round yet.</l>
<l>Being fearful about her with Govinda,</l>
<l rend="indent">my heart is becoming [more] disturbed each day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
